{"tid":450383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★買左點算？如「綠置居」的需求減退，會考慮轉為出租。","createTime":"2017-10-28T06:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T12:36:54.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3fd80a39b68853274aa0bdcae831aa4b0b1fbf24","tid":450383,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:37:06.000Z","msg":"運輸及房屋局局長陳帆指，日後可彈性調配「綠置居」和出租公屋比例：「如果日後推展『綠置居』，市民接受程度很高、或需求很大的話，我們會將數目按部就班調升，但如果去到一個階段，『綠置居』歡迎程度減退或需要不大，餘下建成的公共房屋，亦會轉化為出租公屋。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/59f40ee6e603834c78eb24a7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F59f40ee6e603834c78eb24a7%2F&d=ttNQWDG3zbjj93Fe4ww0CZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a13a1ade\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/59f40ee6e603834c78eb24a7/</a>"},{"pid":"d07784fdf645d133d53ffe862234184b3b9bd2dc","tid":450383,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973a75b51733555f7e04e8df0ac0acf4db5b418b","tid":450383,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:39:10.000Z","msg":"All chi na租户"},{"pid":"40752c0ad37ad71bb9b62accdb1e7e2e5dd484bc","tid":450383,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"如果綠置居座樓有100個單位，只有10個單位俾人買左綠置居，剩低90單位是否又轉公屋or丟空？"},{"pid":"f32e003fee8fcab4d14cd120b1b57164ee6b5c78","tid":450383,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:40:38.000Z","msg":"<bloc